title: Une histoire banale (2014)

cast.name: Frédéric Duff-Barbé
cast.character: Le lieutenant de police       (as Frédéric 'Duff' Barbé)

cast.name: Aurore Broutin
cast.character: La fille agressée dans la rue

overview: Nathalie, 32 years old, is an ordinary woman of her age totally in love with her boyfriend. But her life will totally change when her co-worker rape her after a party. Life is now a struggle where every detail is a fight to get back a normal life. Through this 'ordinary' story, Natalie will turn into an example for all those women who had chosen to remain silent.
